title: Aman Binepal’s Site
text: Welcome to my website! If you want to learn more about me, please navigate to the About page.

title: About
text: My name is Amanpreet Binepal but I go by Aman. I am a student at UBC in the Master of Data Science Program with the goal of pursuing Data Science. I am born and raised in British Columbia specifically Surrey, BC. Before UBC I went to BCIT where I completed a Diploma in Computer Information Technology and a Bachelor’s of Business Administration with a focus in Business Intelligence.
